言論自由的權利。<br />\n<br />\n第二，此法對警員及香港市民雙重標準。<br />\n《禁蒙面法》生效後，一方面是警員依然遮蓋其委任證，甚至戴黑口罩雙重隱瞞身份。另一方面，普通市民連戴衛生口罩出外也隨時被警員截停查問。例如，不少記者被警員扯下其防催淚彈的面罩。（註一）有患癌症的市民展示其醫生紙卻被警員視為偽造文件等。（註二）法例通過後的穩定社會成效未見，但市民對政府和警方的不滿卻再創新高！<br />\n<br />\n因此，禁蒙面法只會增加民憤，完全無法做到預期的止暴制亂的效果。希望政府能順應民意，取消惡法。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民 你個名上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註一：-記者遭警強扯面罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F391108%2F%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%BC%B7%E6%89%AF%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%89-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%84%A1%E7%89%B9%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfvdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=cee78ce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示</a><br />\n<br />\n註二：癌漢戴口罩 警屈偽造醫生紙<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfvdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=86ef7279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI&h=7ec8f2fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI</a><br />\n<br />\n自己自行加減"},{"pid":"3ad52003db853b91f56e5ec9f31af4472131b66a","tid":1692847,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74954c93f05c74228d50f9e6b95cd9322b9635db","tid":1692847,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"甴近平"}]}